ZH: 这个煤矿是我们的主要资源来源。
EN: This coal mine is our main source of resources.

ZH: 煤是一种常见的化石燃料。
EN: Coal is a common fossil fuel.

ZH: 他们在烤箱里加了点煤以加热。
EN: They added some coal to the oven for heating.

ZH: 这堆煤应该可以燃烧很长时间。
EN: This pile of coal should burn for a long time.

ZH: 矿工们将煤从矿井里挖出来。
EN: Miners dig coal out from the mine.

ZH: 煤的产量在过去几年持续增长。
EN: The coal production has been steadily increasing over the past few years.

ZH: 在过去的几十年中，煤一直是主要能源之一。
EN: Coal has been one of the primary energy sources over the past few decades.

ZH: 炼铁厂依赖于大量的煤来生产钢铁。
EN: Steel plants rely on large amounts of coal for production.

ZH: 煤炭污染对环境造成了严重影响。
EN: Coal pollution has had a significant impact on the environment.

ZH: 近年来，政府一直在推动煤的清洁生产。
EN: In recent years, the government has been promoting clean production of coal.

ZH: 煤矿工人面对着高风险和艰苦的工作环境。
EN: Coal miners face high risks and difficult working conditions.

ZH: 这个国家依赖进口煤来满足能源需求。
EN: This country relies on imported coal to meet its energy needs.

ZH: 煤在工业生产中具有重要的地位。
EN: Coal plays an important role in industrial production.

ZH: 煤炭的价格一直在波动。
EN: The price of coal has been fluctuating.

ZH: 煤是一个非常脏的燃料，对环境造成破坏。
EN: Coal is a very dirty fuel that causes damage to the environment.

ZH: 每年有数以千计的矿工死于煤矿事故。
EN: Thousands of miners die in coal mine accidents every year.

ZH: 煤气可以用来烹饪食物。
EN: Coal gas can be used for cooking food.

ZH: 这个国家依靠煤炭来发电。
EN: This country relies on coal for power generation.

ZH: 煤矿工人的工作条件通常很艰苦。
EN: Coal miners often work in harsh conditions.

ZH: 煤可以在电厂中被燃烧以产生电力。
EN: Coal can be burned in power plants to generate electricity.
